name: Add-on Popularity
query:
SELECT
    `tabAirplane Ticket Add-on Item`.item AS `Add-on Type`,
    COUNT(*) AS `Sold Count`
FROM
    `tabAirplane Ticket Add-on Item`
INNER JOIN
    `tabAirplane Ticket`
ON
    `tabAirplane Ticket Add-on Item`.parent = `tabAirplane Ticket`.name
GROUP BY
    `tabAirplane Ticket Add-on Item`.item
ORDER BY
    `Sold Count` DESC;
